ï»؟[{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"## Technical Changes\n- **Stake API Integration**: Fixed payload mapping (snake_case) and serialized amount to string to match backend DTO.\n- **KYC/Security**: Improved error handling to provide specific feedback for 403 Forbidden (KYC required) and 400 Bad Request (Market locked).\n- **Market Models**: Synchronized MarketStatus and MarketCategory with backend values (case-sensitive mapping).\n- **Arena UI**: \n  - Added horizontal navigation buttons for category filters.\n  - Disabled stake button for resolved/locked markets with visual status feedback.\n  - Updated icons and badge styles for all categories.\n- **Testing**: Fixed IDE errors in market-detail.component.spec.ts by including jasmine types.\n\n## Motivation\nResolve the 403/400 errors during staking and ensure the Arena experience is consistent with the backend data structure.\n\n## Tests Performed\n- Validated build-prediction payload via browser console and backend logs.\n- Verified KYC promotion via manual DB update.\n- Tested filter navigation and category icons on multiple viewport sizes.","createdAt":"2026-04-23T20:33:59Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-23T20:34:07Z","number":35,"state":"MERGED","title":"fix: Stake API Integration and Arena UI Refinement","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/35"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"### Description\nThis PR fixes the issue where the market probability history chart was appearing empty or blank on the Market Details page.\n\n### Changes Made\n- **Host Styles**: Added \\:host { display: block; height: 100%; }\\ to \\ProbabilityChartComponent\\ to ensure the container has a valid height for Chart.js rendering.\n- **Data Mapping**: Fixed a mismatch where the chart line was being rendered out of bounds due to an incorrect percentage multiplier (now synchronized with backend fraction changes).\n- **Update Logic**: Enhanced \\\ngOnChanges\\ to trigger chart updates when the time range is switched, ensuring the UI reflects the correct labels and data points immediately.\n- **Backend Sync**: (Coordinated change) Updated the backend to support the \\\range\\ parameter (\\1D\\, \\1W\\, \\ALL\\) sent by the frontend.\n\n### Testing\n- Verified that the chart now renders correctly with a green line.\n- Verified that switching ranges (1D/1W/ALL) updates the chart labels and data.","createdAt":"2026-04-23T19:20:06Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-23T19:20:13Z","number":34,"state":"MERGED","title":"fix(FE-6): fix market probability chart display","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/34"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"## Stake End-to-End Flow (FE-7)\n\nThis PR implements the complete stake flow, from transaction building to real-time confirmation.\n\n### Changes:\n- **StakeService**: Orchestrates the build-sign-submit flow.\n- **Notification System**:\n  - **NotificationService**: Global state for toasts.\n  - **TxToastComponent**: Premium UI with spinners, success/error states, and explorer links.\n  - **NotificationContainerComponent**: Fixed container for multiple toasts.\n- **Real-time Integration**:\n  - **RealtimeService**: WebSocket listener for \\\tx_submitted\\, \\\tx_confirmed\\, and \\\tx_failed\\.\n- **Persistence & Reconciliation**:\n  - **PendingTxStore**: Saves transactions to \\localStorage\\ before signing.\n  - **AppInit Reconciliation**: Checks pending transactions on startup and syncs with backend status.\n- **UI Updates**:\n  - Integrated \\StakeService\\ into \\StakeFormComponent\\.\n  - Added loading states and form validations (auth/amount).\n\n### Visuals:\n- Neutral toast with spinner during build/sign.\n- Green toast on success.\n- Terracotta toast on error/cancel.\n\nCloses #9","createdAt":"2026-04-23T15:23:27Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-23T15:23:34Z","number":33,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat(frontend): FE-7 - Stake end-to-end (build XDR + wallet + optimistic UI)","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/33"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"### Description\nThis PR integrates the frontend with the real backend API running on \\localhost:3000\\. It updates the data structures and models to match the official backend documentation and resolves discrepancies in the authentication and market modules.\n\n### Key Changes\n- **Authentication**:\n    - Updated \\AuthResponse\\ to match backend fields (\\jwt\\, \\user\\).\n    - Fixed \\AuthService\\ login flow to include the missing \\\nonce\\ in the \\/verify\\ request body.\n    - Added data mapping in \\AuthService\\ to maintain compatibility with existing \\AuthProfile\\ usage.\n- **Markets**:\n    - Renamed \\\total_volume\\ to \\\total_liquidity\\, \\lock_ts\\ to \\lock_at\\, and \\\resolve_ts\\ to \\settle_at\\ in the \\Market\\ model.\n    - Updated \\MarketListResponse\\ to handle the backend's new \\pagination\\ object.\n    - Updated \\MarketHistoryResponse\\ to handle the \\snapshots\\ wrapper.\n- **UI & Components**:\n    - Updated \\MarketCardComponent\\ and \\StakeFormComponent\\ to reflect new field names and handle optional price fields safely.\n    - Fixed \\ProbabilityChartComponent\\ to use \\yes_probability\\.\n- **Infrastructure & Mocks**:\n    - Updated \\environment.development.ts\\ to connect to the real API and disable mocks by default.\n    - Refactored \\mock-auth.interceptor.ts\\ and \\mock-market.interceptor.ts\\ to remain consistent with the new real API structures.","createdAt":"2026-04-23T13:58:51Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-23T13:58:59Z","number":32,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat: Real Backend API Integration and Model Adaptation","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/32"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"Centralizes API endpoints using API_CONFIG and versioning from environment.ts. Implements concurrent refresh handling and strict interceptor matching.","createdAt":"2026-04-22T21:12:14Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T21:12:22Z","number":31,"state":"MERGED","title":"chore(frontend): standardizing endpoints with baseURL and versioning (FE-5A)","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/31"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"### Descriâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\nImplementaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o completa da tela de detalhes do mercado (FE-6), incluindo grâ”œأ­fico de probabilidade histâ”œâ”‚rico, formulâ”œأ­rio de stake dinâ”œأ³mico e regras de resoluâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o.\n\n### Mudanâ”œآ؛as Realizadas\n- **NgRx Store**: Criada store de mercado para gerenciamento de estado (aâ”œآ؛â”œأپes, reducers, efeitos e seletores).\n- **Componentes**:\n  - MarketDetailComponent: Layout responsivo otimizado para desktop e mobile.\n  - ProbabilityChartComponent: Integraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o com Chart.js para visualizaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de tendâ”œآ¬ncias.\n  - StakeFormComponent: Formulâ”œأ­rio compacto com câ”œأ­lculo dinâ”œأ³mico de taxas e validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes.\n- **Serviâ”œآ؛os**: Atualizaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o do MarketService para suportar detalhes e histâ”œâ”‚rico.\n- **Mocks**: Expansâ”œأ؛o do interceptor de mock para simular dados realistas de mercado e histâ”œâ”‚rico.\n- **Layout**: Ajustes finos de UX para eliminar scroll desnecessâ”œأ­rio em desktop e corrigir ordem de elementos em mobile.\n\n### Critâ”œآ®rios de Aceite\n- [x] Dados e grâ”œأ­fico renderizam corretamente.\n- [x] Taxas por mercado aparecem no calculador.\n- [x] Estados de loading/erro implementados.\n- [x] Teste unitâ”œأ­rio de toggle de range aprovado.\n\nFixes #8","createdAt":"2026-04-22T18:51:05Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T18:51:21Z","number":30,"state":"MERGED","title":"FE-6: Market Detail (Chart + Resolution + Stake Form)","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/30"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"Implements FE-5: Arena Markets discovery page with search, category filtering, and responsive cards.","createdAt":"2026-04-22T18:12:12Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T18:17:51Z","number":29,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat(frontend): Arena Markets (listing + filters + search)","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/29"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"## FE-4 - Landing (desktop + mobile)\n\nCloses #5\n\n### What's included\n- **HeroSection** - headline, subheadline, animated blob background, card mockup, CTA with 4 wallet states (disconnected / connecting / connected / error)\n- **MetricsBar** - dark branded metrics strip (Distributed, Stakers, Active Arenas, Partner NGOs, Satisfaction)\n- **FeaturesGrid** - 5 feature cards + 4-step flow diagram\n- **ConnectWalletCard** - full-screen CTA with social proof testimonials, all wallet states handled\n- **LandingFooter** - dark footer with Product / Community / Legal columns and Stellar attribution\n- **Wallet modal theme** - custom StakeGood brand theme injected into StellarWalletsKit (dark bg, green primary, Inter font)\n- **AppShell patch** - landing route strips the default 1.5rem shell padding so dark sections go full-width\n- All UI copy in English\n\n### Checklist\n- [x] Hero + CTAs\n- [x] Responsive (960px + 600px breakpoints)\n- [x] Connected / disconnected / connecting / error states\n\n### Branch\nfeature/FE-4-landing -> main\n","createdAt":"2026-04-22T17:58:42Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T17:59:27Z","number":28,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat(frontend): FE-4 - Landing page (desktop + mobile)","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/28"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"Closes #4. Implements NgRx UserState and Auth/KYC/Terms/Role guards as specified in the issue.","createdAt":"2026-04-22T17:03:50Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T17:31:21Z","number":27,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat(frontend): FE-3 - UserState (NgRx) + Guards (Auth/KYC/Terms/Role)","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/27"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"## Descriâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\nEste PR implementa o fluxo completo de autenticaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o Web3 (Issue #3), integrando o login via carteira Stellar com gestâ”œأ؛o de sessâ”œأ؛o segura (JWT) e refresh automâ”œأ­tico de tokens. Alâ”œآ®m disso, unifica este fluxo com a arquitetura de App Shell estabelecida anteriormente, garantindo uma experiâ”œآ¬ncia responsiva e premium em todos os dispositivos.\n\n## Alteraâ”œآ؛â”œأپes Realizadas\n\n### 1. Autenticaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o Web3 (Core)\n- **Fluxo de Login**: Implementado o handshake nonce -> signMessage -> verify utilizando a Stellar Wallets Kit (v2).\n- **Session Management**: Criado o AuthService para gerenciar o estado global de autenticaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o e o AuthStorageService para persistâ”œآ¬ncia segura no localStorage.\n- **Interceptors**:\n    - AuthInterceptor: Injeâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o automâ”œأ­tica de tokens JWT em todas as requisiâ”œآ؛â”œأپes.\n    - **Refresh Automâ”œأ­tico**: O interceptor monitora a expiraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o do token e dispara uma renovaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o silenciosa antes que o token expire, garantindo que fluxos crâ”œآ،ticos nâ”œأ؛o sejam interrompidos.\n- **Mock System**: Implementado o MockAuthInterceptor (ativado via flag de ambiente) para simular o backend e facilitar o desenvolvimento offline.\n\n### 2. Integraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o com App Shell\n- **Sincronizaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o**: O trabalho da FE-2 foi unificado com a FE-1, restaurando a Sidebar e a navegaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o em camadas.\n- **WalletConnect Component**: Criado um componente dedicado e reutilizâ”œأ­vel para conexâ”œأ؛o de carteira com estados de carregamento, erro e exibiâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de perfil.\n\n### 3. UI/UX e Responsividade\n- **Layout Desktop**: Carteira integrada ao rodapâ”œآ® da Sidebar com design de Profile Card premium.\n- **Layout Mobile (Hamburger Drawer)**:\n    - Navegaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o centralizada em um menu lateral (Drawer) deslizante.\n    - Otimizaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de espaâ”œآ؛o: Remoâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o da Bottom Bar em favor de um cabeâ”œآ؛alho mais limpo com â”œآ،cone de menu.\n- **Global Reset**: Implementaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de reset CSS para eliminar scrolls indesejados e garantir consistâ”œآ¬ncia visual.\n- **Aesthetics**: Uso de gradientes, sombras suaves, micro-animaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes (spinners) e tipografia Inter.\n\n### 4. Configuraâ”œآ؛â”œأپes de Ambiente\n- Suporte nativo para **TESTNET** e **FUTURENET**.\n- Flag useMock adicionada aos arquivos de environment.ts para alternar facilmente entre modo simulado e API real.\n\n## Validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes\n- [x] Login completo funciona (nonce -> assinatura -> JWT).\n- [x] Refresh de token automâ”œأ­tico validado no console.\n- [x] Navegaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o funcional no Desktop (Sidebar) e Mobile (Drawer).\n- [x] Logout limpa sessâ”œأپes locais e desconecta a carteira.\n- [x] Build de produâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o passando sem erros.\n\n## Documentaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\n- Criado arquivo how-to-run.md detalhando como configurar o ambiente e alternar entre os modos Mock/API.","createdAt":"2026-04-22T15:58:44Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T16:18:06Z","number":26,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat(frontend): FE-2 - Login Web3 (nonce + assinatura + authenticate + refresh)","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/26"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"## Descriâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\nEste PR implementa a integraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o real com a rede Stellar/Soroban atravâ”œآ®s do **Stellar Wallets Kit (SWK) v2** no `WalletService`. Substituâ”œآ،mos os stubs iniciais por uma lâ”œâ”‚gica agnâ”œâ”‚stica de carteira que suporta os principais provedores da rede.\n\n## Mudanâ”œآ؛as Principais\n- **Core Service**: \n  - Refatoraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o completa do `WalletService` utilizando a API estâ”œأ­tica do SWK v2.\n  - Gerenciamento de estado reativo com `BehaviorSubject` para a chave pâ”œâ•‘blica.\n  - Suporte nativo a **Freighter, Albedo, xBull e WalletConnect**.\n  - Lâ”œâ”‚gica de persistâ”œآ¬ncia e reconexâ”œأ؛o automâ”œأ­tica via `sessionStorage`.\n- **Compatibilidade**:\n  - Adicionados polyfills de `Buffer` e `global` no `main.ts` para garantir o funcionamento do `stellar-sdk` em ambiente browser (Vite/Angular).\n- **Interface (UI)**:\n  - `TopBarComponent` atualizado com estâ”œآ®tica premium (glassmorphism, gradientes).\n  - Adicionado indicador visual de status da conexâ”œأ؛o (status dot).\n  - Implementado botâ”œأ؛o de desconexâ”œأ؛o funcional que limpa totalmente o estado do kit e do navegador.\n- **Transaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes**:\n  - `TxService` agora utiliza o mâ”œآ®todo `sign()` do `WalletService` para solicitar assinaturas reais dos usuâ”œأ­rios.\n\n## Critâ”œآ®rios de Aceite / Checklist\n- [x] Modal do Kit abre corretamente ao clicar em \"Connect\".\n- [x] O endereâ”œآ؛o da carteira â”œآ® exibido de forma abreviada na interface apâ”œâ”‚s o login.\n- [x] A desconexâ”œأ؛o â”œآ® limpa e permite selecionar uma carteira diferente na prâ”œâ”‚xima tentativa.\n- [x] O sistema injeta polyfills necessâ”œأ­rios para evitar erros de runtime com o SDK da Stellar.\n- [x] O `TxService` estâ”œأ­ pronto para consumir o fluxo de assinatura.\n\nFixes #24\n","createdAt":"2026-04-22T14:21:05Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T14:28:17Z","number":25,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat(core): integraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o do Stellar Wallets Kit (SWK) no WalletService","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/25"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"# Descriâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\nEste PR implementa a fundaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o tâ”œآ®cnica do frontend do StakeGood (Issue #1), estabelecendo o App Shell, a arquitetura em camadas e o sistema de design base.\n\n## Alteraâ”œآ؛â”œأپes Realizadas\n### 1. App Shell e Layout Responsivo\n- **AppShellComponent**: Container principal que orquestra a exibiâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o da TopBar, SideBar e MainContent.\n- **TopBar**: Cabeâ”œآ؛alho fixo com branding e botâ”œأ؛o de \"Connect Wallet\" (integrado ao `WalletService`).\n- **SideBar**: Navegaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o lateral para desktop com estados ativos e hover.\n- **BottomBar**: Navegaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o inferior otimizada para dispositivos mâ”œâ”‚veis.\n- **Responsividade**: Layout adaptâ”œأ­vel que alterna entre SideBar (desktop) e BottomBar (mobile), com bloqueio de viewport para evitar scrolls indesejados.\n\n### 2. Arquitetura em Camadas (UI/Services/Web3)\n- **Camada de Serviâ”œآ؛os**: Criados stubs e contratos iniciais em `core/services/` para:\n  - `AuthService`: Gestâ”œأ؛o de estado de autenticaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o.\n  - `WalletService`: Integraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o com carteiras Web3 (Stellar/Soroban).\n  - `MarketService`: Abstraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de dados de mercados.\n  - `TxService`: Manipulaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de transaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes e XDRs.\n- **Separaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de Preocupaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes**: Componentes UI agora consomem dados apenas via serviâ”œآ؛os, sem lâ”œâ”‚gica Web3 direta.\n\n### 3. Design System & Tokens\n- **Design Tokens**: Implementaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de variâ”œأ­veis CSS (`--primary-color`, `--bg-color`, etc.) no `styles.css`.\n- **Global Reset**: Limpeza de margens/paddings padrâ”œأ؛o e configuraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de `box-sizing: border-box`.\n- **Estâ”œآ®tica Premium**: Aplicaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de cores `#11D48A` (primâ”œأ­ria), `#F6F8F7` (fundo) e `#111815` (texto), com border-radius de 12-16px e sombras leves.\n\n### 4. Roteamento e Navegaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\n- Configuraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de rotas base:\n  - `/landing` (Pâ”œâ•‘blica)\n  - `/arena` (Protegida - Placeholder)\n  - `/profile` (Protegida - Placeholder)\n- Uso de `loadComponent` para Lazy Loading de rotas.\n\n## Validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes\n- [x] Navegaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o funcional entre rotas.\n- [x] Ausâ”œآ¬ncia de scroll vertical em pâ”œأ­ginas com pouco conteâ”œâ•‘do.\n- [x] Ajuste de espaâ”œآ؛amento no menu vertical conforme feedback do usuâ”œأ­rio.\n- [x] Smoke test (`app.spec.ts`) passando via Vitest.\n\n---\n**Branch**: `feature/FE-1-app-shell`  \n**Issue Relacionada**: #1\n","createdAt":"2026-04-22T13:28:20Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T13:29:25Z","number":23,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat(frontend): FE-1 - App Shell + Arquitetura em camadas","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/23"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"## Proposta\nConfiguraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o inicial do frontend para interaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o com a rede Stellar.\n\n## Mudanâ”œآ؛as Realizadas\n- **Bootstrap Angular**: Inicializado projeto com Angular 17/21 (Standalone, Signals, Roteamento e CSS Vanilla).\n- **Integraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o Stellar**: Instalaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o e configuraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o do @stellar/stellar-sdk e @albedo-link/intent.\n- **Arquitetura**:\n  - Configuraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de aliases @core e @shared no \tsconfig.json.\n  - Criaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de diretâ”œâ”‚rios estruturados (services, models, guards, components, etc).\n- **Core Service**: \n  - StellarService criado para abstrair chamadas â”œأ، Horizon.\n  - Uso de **Signals** para rastreamento de estado da conexâ”œأ؛o.\n- **Ambientes**: Configuraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de environment para Futurenet (padrâ”œأ؛o) e Testnet.\n- **Correâ”œآ؛â”œأپes/Polimento**:\n  - Remoâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de warnings de CommonJS no build (^GllowedCommonJsDependencies).\n  - Ajuste de budgets para comportar o SDK.\n  - UI bâ”œأ­sica de status criada no AppComponent.\n\n## Validaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\n- [x] Build efetuado com sucesso (\npm run build).\n- [x] \ng serve executado sem erros.\n- [x] Importaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes do Stellar SDK corrigidas para padrâ”œأپes de versâ”œأ؛o recente (Horizon.Server).\n\nFixes #21","createdAt":"2026-04-22T12:50:18Z","mergedAt":"2026-04-22T12:50:35Z","number":22,"state":"MERGED","title":"feat: project setup (Angular + Stellar SDK) #21","url":"https://github.com/StakeGood-UFMT/frontend/pull/22"}]
